   "source": [
    "# FinBERT Pipeline\n",
    "**Course:** CS-4267-02 Deep Learning  \n",
    "**Author:** Simon Gou\n",
    "\n",
    "End-to-end pipeline:\n",
    "1. GPU check\n",
    "2. Environment setup (clone repo, mount Drive)\n",
    "3. Load transcript data\n",
    "4. Compute CAR labels\n",
    "5. FinBERT inference (with checkpointing)\n",
    "6. Visualize sentiment distributions\n",
    "7. Train prediction head (4 variants)\n",
    "8. Results & financial metrics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b2c3d4e5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. GPU Check"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "c3d4e5f6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"GPU available : {torch.cuda.is_available()}\")\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print(f\"GPU name      : {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}\")\n",
    "    mem_gb = torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_memory / 1e9\n",
    "    print(f\"GPU memory    : {mem_gb:.1f} GB\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"WARNING: No GPU detected. Inference will be very slow on CPU.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d4e5f6g7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
